86 (D) In the absence of an approved report, the chairperson shall file with the Clerk of
87 the House of Representatives a copy of the minutes of the meetings of the committee
88 in lieu thereof.
89 (7) Abolishment. The committee shall stand abolished on December 1, 2025.
